{"tid":971240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「超級血狼月」現身　猶太預警：將有強大國家倒台","createTime":"2019-01-06T13:11:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T13:39:47.000Z","uid":54373,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ebb7249d8f954fa5ad684027f0c474c2f0d04c","tid":971240,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/01/06/20190106175759-f90b8248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F06%2F20190106175759-f90b8248.jpg&h=8110319d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本月的滿月之時會發生月全蝕，天空中將上演結合「超級月亮」、「血月」和「狼月」三大特色的天文奇觀「超級血狼月」(super blood wolf moon)。對此，有猶太教拉比(rabbi，指猶太教律法專家)表示，這是在預告有些看似強大的政府會垮台，有些政府則會興盛起來。<br />\n <br />\n據美國國家航空航天局(NASA)的資料顯示，1月21日凌晨12點12分的「超級血狼月」只會在北美、南美地區，以及歐洲西部和非洲部份地區看得到，而在亞洲、澳洲、印度和靠近亞洲的多數太平洋島嶼，因這時間是在白晝，將無法一窺3年來再次出現的奇景。<br />\n <br />\n據以色列突發新聞(Breaking Israel News)網站報導，21日的「超級血狼月」剛好是在猶太習俗中4個傳統新年之一的「猶太植樹節」(Tu B&rsquo;shva)，也就是希伯來曆細罷特月(Shevat)的第15天，在如此難得一見的月亮徵兆出現時，意味著「萬物的結局近了」。<br />\n <br />\n猶太教的傑出拉比格納特(Mordechai Genut)，曾出書探討月蝕在猶太教中所代表的意義。他提出警示表示，在細罷特月出現月蝕，即代表著世界的災難將會快速升級，像是地震和火山爆發會明顯增加，甚至比去年還多。格納特表示，正如月蝕是太陽和月亮為了支配天空所產生的衝突現象，在地上也會有類似的衝突，有些現在看起來很強大的國家將會垮台，有些國家則會興盛起來。<br />\n<br />\n依據猶太教的經典解讀日蝕和月蝕顯示，日蝕對於所有國家而言都是壞預兆，至於月蝕，如果月球在月蝕發生期間變紅色，就像這個月即將發生的「血月」一樣，這預示著世界上會發生大戰。"},{"pid":"f1d5312603742372fa875df42848b31e486f3207","tid":971240,"uid":7741,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:12:11.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5585aefed243fd85047600221f6782fd2257f0c7","tid":971240,"uid":94828,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"倒台一定係美國 中國成為世界霸主 又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2df5148f0c03ebe01c1a4c19e56ea1c05e9617","tid":971240,"uid":107364,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:14:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3db50ea8ddae005e97cd6e0c9698a61e8629b14b","tid":971240,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fcc09f9e9ed3df6b2dd1dc3fb7b90871f6f4e0","tid":971240,"uid":60297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:14:49.000Z","msg":"2012 世界末日"},{"pid":"c83831d7c3e023849d1e43a454229cfa34370814","tid":971240,"uid":108337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:15:24.000Z","msg":"看起來很強大<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a14cbf17ff15e70837496380e3352fc3982833","tid":971240,"uid":164961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"薩爾達傳說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ca1124a7082c4adaa85d1b220fe3aa8dfaa84e","tid":971240,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"可能係指緊法國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n馬克龍 就快收皮"},{"pid":"6f230ddcef45263f9ae9e12553edfbbcddca7ef0","tid":971240,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92a14cbf17ff15e70837496380e3352fc3982833","tid":971240,"uid":164961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"薩爾達傳說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:17:11.000Z","msg":"海拉爾大陸淪陷 魔王征服世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6131c8efd7f64233ddb3ea0cc74ed323538835c","tid":971240,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:33:40.000Z",